data.description: Nestled in the heart of picturesque Snohomish, this 3bed/1bath home with a newly installed roof is a gem. The lush garden that welcomes you in is like stepping into your own private retreat as you arrive. Through the front door, a large living room with modern electric fireplace is the perfect room to get cozy. The kitchen boasts ample storage with country charm next to a large dining room. Step outside onto a large, freshly stained, partially covered deck from which you can enjoy the views of the greenbelt. Beyond the deck, walk the garden path to a beautiful gazebo and listen to the trickle of water from the fountain. This home boasts a large one car garage with additional space for storage, if the three hallway closets won’t suffice.
